</p>
<p>30. Rowell Delgado, 24, a worker for Toyota Motor Philippines, a member of the 
TMPCWA. He suffered abrasions to his body. 
</p>
<p>31. Rolando Mingo, 52, chairman of the Southern Tagalog Region Transport Sector 
Organization (STARTER) and Vice- Chairman ng Pinag-isang Lakas ng Transport 
